Automated Monitoring System Version 3.1 [AMS 3.1]
Usage: ams [options...] <name>
 -a, --about        Show about file
 -c, --create       create a new kpi with the mentioned name
 -d, --delete 	    delete the mentioned kpi
 -e, --edit 	    edit the mentioned kpi
 -g, --gui	    activate/deactivate GUI for AMS
 -h, --help	    Show help file
 -l, --log	    Show log file for mentioned kpi
 -M, --manual       Show AMS manual
 -p, --stop	    stop the mentioned kpis
 -s, --start	    start the mentioned kpis
 
 for more help :
 ams --help [create | delete | edit | conf | stop | start | test | gui]
